sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant GQL as GraphQL Server
    participant R as Resolver Layer
    participant DS as Data Source

    C->>GQL: POST /graphql { query, variables }
    GQL->>GQL: Parse query string to AST
    alt Parse error
        GQL-->>C: 400 Syntax Error
    else Parse success
        GQL->>GQL: Validate AST against schema
        alt Validation error
            GQL-->>C: 400 Validation Error
        else Validation success
            GQL->>GQL: Build execution plan
            GQL->>R: Dispatch root field resolvers
            R->>DS: Query database / call service
            DS-->>R: Return raw data
            R->>R: Resolve nested fields
            R->>DS: Fetch related records
            DS-->>R: Return related data
            R-->>GQL: Resolver results map
            GQL->>GQL: Merge results into response shape
            GQL-->>C: 200 OK with data object and errors array
        end
    end
